ceu com Celso e a condiçăo para năo o entregar ŕ polícia é que Fausto conte como a măe foi incriminada." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="3175000" grandparentArt="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentRatingKey="687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentThumb="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/wedotv_amor_piel_salvaje20630_1672565-portrait.jpg" grandparentTitle="Piel Salvaje" grandparentType="show" index="102" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg" title="S01E102" userState="0"><Image alt="S01E102" type="coverArt" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg"/><Image alt="S01E102" type="coverPoster" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/wedotv_amor_piel_salvaje20630_1672565-portrait.jpg"/><Image alt="S01E102" type="snapshot" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1776917458" duration="3175000" endsAt="1776920633" id="69df8542ec0d2bce0f457cd5" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776936220" duration="3175000" endsAt="1776939395" id="69e0d6a68964ff5aa8990876" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776957886" duration="3175000" endsAt="1776961061" id="69e0d6a68964ff5aa899087d" onAir="1" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776979552" duration="3175000" endsAt="1776982727" id="69e0d6a68964ff5aa8990884" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoRes